name: Based Butthole
description: Directly from our website's about section. Nobody can fart without having a butthole, right? We are a CTO of Based Butthole. The original developer prompted the creation of the token using Clanker's Token Bot. All Clanker releases are fair launches with no allocations for devs or insiders. Everyone has a fair chance to buy on the open market. It does however, reward the developer wallet with fee rewards in the form of ETH and supply of the token, in this case Based Butthole. The original dev couldn't pass the fart from their butthole, so they abandoned this coin just before hitting one million market cap after 2 days. With the help of the clanker developers, we reverted all of the fee rewards to a new multi-signature wallet, and all reward proceeds now only go towards project investments!
